### Track — page_view
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "user-123",
  "event_type": "page_view",
  "properties": {
    "page": "/home",
    "referrer": "google.com"
  },
  "context": {
    "device": "mobile",
    "session_id": "sess-abc"
  }
}

